4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with essential skills in technologies such as JavaScript and Python. Over 18 weeks, participants will learn web development, algorithm scripting, and how to build applications using front-end libraries and APIs. The program includes 16 weeks of coursework and 2 weeks for project development, with classes held three times a week and a low student-to-instructor ratio of 7:1. No prior coding experience is necessary, and instruction is available in both English and Spanish. Graduates receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more info, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop